description: Returns the container images that are registered to your Amazon Lightsail container service.

parameters.name: serviceName
parameters.description: The name of the container service for which to return registered container images.

nested_items.name: containerImages
nested_items.description: An array of objects that describe container images that are registered to the container service.

nested_items.name: image
nested_items.description: The name of the container image.

nested_items.name: digest
nested_items.description: The digest of the container image.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the container image was created.
